x d&rsquo;√©l√©ments √©ditoriaux dans WordPress en fran√ßais :</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Publication est le nom donn√© √† un √©l√©ment g√©n√©rique Post, regroupant donc les articles, les pages et tout autre <em>Custom Post Type (CPT)</em>. Auparavant traduit <em>¬´ Type de contenu personnalis√© ¬ª</em>, <em>¬´ Custom Post Type ¬ª</em> devient <em>¬´ Type de publication personnalis√© ¬ª</em>.</li><li>Chaque publication (article, page, autres CPT) poss√®de une <strong>zone de contenu</strong>, qu&rsquo;il s&rsquo;agisse de l&rsquo;√©diteur Classique ou des Blocs du nouvel √©diteur.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/team/files/2018/07/publications-1.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:114:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2018/12/04/wp-5-0-modification-de-traduction-du-terme-generique-post-en-publication/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"WordPress 5.0 version beta 1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2018/10/27/wordpress-5-0-version-beta-1/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_expl